_aLatestUpdates._sText:
Because of all the traction this has been getting, I thought I would add a bonus map. This is mostly a test for the devneon textures I was using, but it was also the leftovers of ideas I had from bhop_for_blank.

I also added signatures to the end of both maps, because when KawaiiClan was playing it, i had to tell everybody that it was my map, instead of them knowing who made it, and then referring to me.

_sText:
This map is HEAVILY inspired by the glow map series, (purpleglow, redglow, greenglow) and I thank the map creator, Nallieheai, for helping me out with the skyboxes. It is much easier than my other maps. For the first time in my mapmaking "career" I've also made a map with stages. There are 6 stages in total of varying difficulty. 

WARNING: The stages are absolutely NOT straightforward. Don't worry if you get lost at some point. 

Length: 40 seconds to 1 minute
Difficulty: Easy - Medium


HUGE thanks to GAMMACASE for helping me out with the glowing neon textures. Without him/her I would've never figured it out and the textures would look a LOT worse.
